\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?r\u233?n siy\u233?m ta tamb\u233?n, Fol. Y\u233?nd w\u233?motai m\u233?n\u225?t Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?rot. Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh siy\u233?m yau y\u233?nmorm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?nta o \u225?roene si muyata, w\u233?nde k\u233?tam\u233? Yesu Keriso a Af\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, emo Yesu yanoi k\u233?rta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Y\u233?nd a tane f\u250?tar y\u233?nmatembang\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?r\u233?n f\u233?fefaf, Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n Galasia yuwom\u233?.
