N\u225?k k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? y\u233?nd k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n n\u225?kfaf m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?neyot so w\u233?morang gh\u233?rs\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Y\u233?nd t\u233? k\u233?r w\u233?morm\u233?n Kerisof\u233? y\u225?ne wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?nan, a y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? yau f\u233?w\u233?m efe gh\u233?rs\u233? w\u233?m, w\u233?nde Keriso efe tafaf y\u233?mor. Y\u233?n\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?nd w\u233?mor s\u233?nonjo fifiyan, y\u233?nd sw\u233?mor ndimbal mwighaye Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene Ambum k\u233?nj\u250?n, emon wuwetam y\u233?nd a waramai y\u225?njo gh\u233?rs\u233? tayot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Y\u233?ndon yau y\u233?kmetan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ng\u225?r\u225?m t\u233?ndot. W\u233?nde njam n\u225?k ew\u233?retam s\u225?i y\u233?ny\u225?tota mbarkand Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233?, Kerisoene k\u233?r siy\u233?m fifiofnar!
