F\u233?m mwigh\u233? ong\u233?n Galasia \u225?r! Efe norayai ngam\u233? si f\u233?fefaf? F\u233?fene gh\u233?kfan saf\u233?nro t\u233?morw\u233?n Yesu Kerisoene k\u233?r wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?nan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Kwaufrongi ta y\u233?n\u233? \u225?mbiro yamm\u233?n: F\u233?mofem Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r sianay\u233?nd m\u233?naye n\u225?koene \u225?s\u225?foghe, o efalo y\u225?toghe n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?m k\u225?y\u225?retati? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
