M\u233?inyotio f\u233?fene matyam fifiofnar emorm\u233?n? Efalofifi y\u233?na f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?m! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r y\u233?ramai f\u233?fefaf a s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam tawafrotau f\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewafrotam y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mofem ewaitotati n\u225?k, o m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd mer si a efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Kemnangi Ebraamenem\u233?n. Buk si noraye, "Y\u233?mon Ng\u225?nj\u225?n efalo yiy\u225?toi, a m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?ne ndimbal mwigham\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yumyoi f\u225? mbark\u225?nd \u225?rm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?yo f\u233?m fiya kawayamngongi nden\u233? Ebraamene efalo \u225?ki ambum y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r em endefene ewam ndimbal mwigh\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Buk si noraye nden\u233?, soram\u233? yuwon Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so t\u225?kmang\u233? T\u233?ndo \u225?r mbark\u225?nd y\u233?fene ndimbal mwigham\u233?n. Buk si norayai y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? yum\u233?n mer si Ebraamefaf, "Fe k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so efrende m\u233?inyotio \u225?r." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde Ebraam\u233?m efalo yiy\u225?toi a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?frendai, y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n m\u233?inyotio emofem efalo yiy\u225?totat freng\u233?ghan em nden\u233? Ebraam k\u233?s t\u233?morw\u233?n.
