F\u225? efe n\u225?myotat n\u225?k \u225?y\u225?r\u233?ghan so emor Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene wafalngogh mbanmbanan. F\u233?yo Buk si noraye, "Emon yau t\u250?m\u233?n n\u225?y\u225?rete m\u233?inyotio yam \u225?rk\u233? ekai n\u225?k bukan siy\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene wafalngogh mbanmbanan!" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
M\u233? saf\u233?nro y\u233?m \u225?rk\u233? \u225?r yau so Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam mbark\u225?nd t\u225?y\u225?tong\u233? y\u233?maf\u233? m\u233?naye n\u225?ke, m\u233?nam\u233?n Buk si noraye, "Mbark\u225?nd \u225?r so emor ndimbal mwighaye." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
W\u233?nde n\u225?k yau y\u233?kai ndimbal mwighafaf. W\u233?ndende Buk si noraye, "Emo njam ewafrota m\u233?inyotio yam n\u225?k ndern\u225?ye noraye so gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?m." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Kerisom y\u233?nmanjary\u233?ng k\u233?tam\u233? n\u225?koene wafalngoghta m\u233?naye f\u225? n\u233?namnday\u233?ng wafalngogh t\u233?feyot, m\u233?nam\u233?n Buk si noraye, "Efe njam tamangi w\u233?nan f\u225? siy\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene wafalngoghan." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?mon y\u233?nmanjary\u233?ng y\u233?nd m\u233?n\u225?t nden\u233? freng\u233?gh \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?ramai Ebraame so y\u233?n\u233?m T\u233?ndo \u225?rfefaf Keriso Yesue k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, m\u233?n\u225?t ndimbal mwighaye y\u233?ndfem s\u225?i tanang\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r Ng\u225?nj\u225?n \u225?rk\u233? uny\u233?ghofnar si norayai.
