Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, y\u233?ndon so t\u233?nmanan m\u233?inyotio efoghm\u233?n wafroghyam. Njam s\u243?mbio \u225?r kuwangend n\u233?m\u233? mwigh\u233? \u225?mbiro tiy\u225?tend, emo yau so t\u233?rafarng\u233? o yau so t\u233?minang\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam uny\u233?ghofnar si korayau Ebraamefaf a y\u225?njo \u225?ki ambumoefaf. Buk si yau nden\u233? noraye, "\u225?ki ambumafefaf, " y\u225?ne fifi t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r, w\u233?nde '\u225?ki ambumoefaf,' y\u225?ne fifi \u225?mbiro \u225?r efe y\u233?m Keriso. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
