Y\u233?nd so namotam: N\u233?mam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam eramai y\u225?njo n\u225?k k\u233?t\u225?n y\u225?ne \u225?r\u233?t? Y\u233?mo eramai y\u233?n\u233? n\u225?k y\u233?feyot m\u233?n\u225?t so tawauyafotau y\u233?fe n\u233?m\u233? yam tamorw\u233?n m\u225?m\u225?fi. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewaramai y\u233?n\u233? n\u225?k k\u233?t\u225?notio Ebraamene \u225?mbiro \u225?kiambum nufary\u233?ng. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?ramai y\u233?n\u233? n\u225?k njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n Mosesefaf. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233?mndetau Moses, a Moses\u233?m tawarametau Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si \u225?r\u233?t. F\u225? namndai n\u233?ndk\u233?f \u225?r Ng\u225?nj\u225?n a \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
W\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yaramai y\u225?njo uny\u233?ghofnar si Ebraame mbark\u225?nde. F\u225? m\u233?ndefnar t\u233?morw\u233?n n\u233?ndk\u233?f \u225?r.
