F\u233?yo k\u233?t\u233? \u225?mb yau f\u233?nataye y\u233?m y\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n Ju \u225?r a T\u233?ndo \u225?r, y\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r a yuwek \u225?r, y\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n \u225?r ghak\u233?r a amaf. F\u233?m m\u233?inyotio sem \u225?mbiro Keriso Yesue k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
