Y\u233?n\u233? ende y\u233?mo y\u233?ny\u225?toi yuwek n\u225?k muyata, m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?nd s\u225?i k\u233?namndangay\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
