S\u233?nonjo f\u233?m mat namndangi Ng\u225?nj\u225?n. O y\u233?nd korayang\u233?n, s\u233?nonjo nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n mat namnda f\u233?m efe em. N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m so ngangongi w\u233?ikor a w\u233?i k\u233?namndangi faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r k\u233?t\u225?n muyafnar a fifiofnar mb\u233?rmb\u233?rfaf y\u233?n\u233? mband maratan? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?mofem eut\u233?mndati wafarer\u233?gh kw\u233?f, gh\u233?rare, w\u233?r\u233?w\u233?r\u233?, a yunj\u233?f. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?nd m\u225?m\u233? mwigh\u233? kw\u233?m f\u233?fenem\u233?n. Y\u233?nd m\u233?ndefnar w\u233?m tane k\u233?rt\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh f\u233?feyot s\u225?i y\u233?m fifiofnar.
