Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, nden\u233? aem y\u233?nd sw\u233?m. Y\u233?ndon ewamnendan f\u233?m, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd njam f\u233?maf\u233? t\u233?nmorw\u233?n, y\u233?nd n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?n nden\u233? f\u233?m. F\u233?mofem n\u233?m\u233? yaufi yau tafrotati tafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u233?m t\u225?f nawafarotati nden\u233? y\u233?nd w\u233?nmorm\u233?n f\u233?fefaf fronde m\u233?nam\u233?n enjne kw\u233?morw\u233?n. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u225?f y\u233?morm\u233?n y\u233?ndo fronde yaitotam\u233?n mer si f\u233?fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?ndo k\u233?rtat ekmay\u233?n f\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?yan enjne kw\u233?morw\u233?n, f\u233?mofem y\u233?nd yau t\u233?kr\u225?taye w\u233?ramay\u233?nd a w\u233?kenay\u233?nd. W\u233?nde f\u233?mofem wumyoy\u233?nd nden\u233? kar kw\u233?morw\u233?n njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r Ng\u225?nj\u225?neta, nden\u233? y\u233?nd kar kw\u233?morw\u233?n Keriso Yesu. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?m minde \u225?uw\u233?ghan tamorw\u233?n! N\u233?m\u233? yam nufrotam? Y\u233?nd y\u233?ndio so korayang\u233?n nden\u233?, y\u233?n\u233? efghon, f\u233?m njam f\u233?yotaro tamorw\u233?n tautorngay\u233?nd f\u233?fenjo gh\u233?k\u233?f, f\u233?mofem so tanramangay\u233?nd tafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
W\u233?nde s\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd namndan f\u233?fene m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r m\u233?naye efalo si afroghe?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r\u233?m yuyafotat k\u233?njkame tik\u233?f f\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n, w\u233?nde y\u233?fene mwigh\u233? faror\u233?gh siy\u233?m yau kor mer y\u233?m. Y\u233?fene m\u233?nde siy\u233?m f\u233?m s\u225?i tafalongi ta tamb\u233?n, m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?mofem so ey\u225?retati f\u225?ro. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Efe njam m\u233?nde y\u233?m f\u233?fefaf meryam wafrogh\u233?t, y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?yotaro y\u233?m, a y\u233?mofem ayafrotat m\u233?inyotio efghon, yau t\u225?fandro y\u233?nd f\u233?maf\u233? njam y\u233?n\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Tane tikfaf\u233? ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r, y\u233?nd nemnan nden\u233? y\u233?nd w\u233?ikor w\u233?m ndenanit ambum \u225?r\u225?f\u233?gh t\u233?kr\u225?t k\u233?nj\u250?n f\u233?feyot k\u233?t\u225?notio f\u233?m t\u233? n\u233?namnday\u233?nd Kerisoene efalo waitogh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Y\u233?nd minde m\u233?nde w\u233?m s\u225?i w\u233?m k\u233?t\u233? f\u233?fefaf s\u233?nonjo. F\u233?yo y\u233?nd so mer mat w\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? so norayan f\u233?fefaf. Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233?, y\u233?nd mafina w\u233?m ndern\u225?ye so kor nemnan f\u233?fenem\u233?n.
