Kwaufrongi, f\u233?m efe m\u233?nde em n\u225?k mbanmbanan s\u225?i em, f\u233?m yau mat em ndern\u225?ye n\u225?k noraye? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Nden\u233? noraye Ebraam t\u233?morw\u233?n s\u243?mbio ambumaf\u233?, \u225?mb faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh amam\u233?n, \u225?mb amaffifim\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh amam\u233?n ambum n\u225?r\u225?ftam fifi ende, w\u233?nde yuwek amafm\u233?n ambum n\u225?r\u225?ftam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene uny\u233?ghofnar si k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? s\u243?mbio amafam yufarot s\u243?mbio \u225?rny\u233?gh. Fronde amaf, Agar\u233?m, yufarote Sainai mband tunak\u233?f \u225?nde \u225?r\u233?m n\u225?k ewanay\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? n\u225?k \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam t\u225?y\u225?totau faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Agar, emo yufarote Sainai mband tunak\u233?f Arabia yuwon, a yufarote s\u233?nonjo ndimbal tesen Jerusalem, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? y\u225?njo ambumaf\u233? emor n\u225?koene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?foghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
W\u233?nde njafarm\u233?n Jerusalem siy\u233?m yuwek, a f\u225? siy\u233?m t\u233?fene am\u233? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
