Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, f\u233?m em uny\u233?ghofnar sim\u233?n ambum, nden\u233? Aisek. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efghon ambum efe n\u225?r\u225?ftam fifie tas\u233?rmbotaw\u233?t ambum efe n\u225?r\u225?ftam Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r waftaye, w\u233?i s\u233?nonjo nden\u233?yameyo fiy\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
W\u233?nde ndern\u225?ye Buk si noraye? Nden\u233? noraye, "T\u233?ngwatem faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh amaf a y\u225?njo ambum, m\u233?nam\u233?n faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh amafoene ambumom yau so tawanang\u233? y\u225?refane rokar y\u233?maf\u233? amaffifioene ambumof\u233?." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
