Kerisom t\u233? efalo y\u233?ny\u225?toy\u233?ng yuwek. S\u233?nonjo kamndangi f\u233?m yuwek, a yau w\u233?ikor kaumbangi n\u225?koene faiofnar sifayat.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
K\u225?y\u225?rangi! Y\u233?ndo, Fol\u233?m, emndetan nden\u233? f\u233?m njam karamangi gh\u233?ngan n\u233?fgh\u233?t, y\u225?ne fifi siy\u233?m Keriso so y\u233?m fifiofnar f\u233?fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
\u193?mbirotaro y\u233?ndon emndetan efe \u225?r kamyong\u233? gh\u233?ngan n\u233?fgh\u233?t, y\u233?mo so ewaitote m\u233?inyotio n\u225?k. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u233?m efe njam kufngongi mbark\u225?ndot Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? n\u225?k waitoghe, f\u233?m t\u233? nanfangi k\u233?tam\u233? Kerisoe tamb\u233?n. F\u233?m sem t\u233?ndon Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ng\u225?r\u225?mta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
W\u233?nde t\u233?feyot, t\u233?fene m\u233?ghm\u233?gh siy\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so mbark\u225?nd y\u233?maf\u233? t\u233?ny\u225?tong\u233? y\u233?nd. Y\u233?n\u233? fiy\u233?m n\u233?mat y\u233?nd nawanjetam m\u233?naye Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r n\u225?s\u225?fota t\u233?fene ndimbal mwigh\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
T\u225?f y\u233?nd njam y\u233?n\u233?m Keriso Yesue k\u233?nj\u250?n, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n yau mwigh\u233? y\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?nd t\u233?u gh\u233?ngan y\u233?n\u233?nfetat o yau. Ndimbal yam siy\u233?m nden\u233? t\u233?fene ndimbal mwigham Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n so y\u233?fune m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i euwetam \u225?mb \u225?r.
