F\u233?m stam mere k\u233?rsati! Emo em\u233?indai ekmbogh\u233?t efalo waitoghta? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam, emo f\u233?m emotai, y\u233?n\u233? yau yafrotam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
\u193?r norayay\u233?nd, "N\u233?mbne flaw\u233? minaghm\u233?n n\u225?s\u225?fote m\u233?inyotio flawayan." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
