Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, y\u233?nd m\u233? njam n\u233?ngorayan nden\u233? f\u233?m so gh\u233?ngan enfetat, n\u233?mam\u233?n Ju \u225?r\u233?m was\u233?rmbotat? Njam y\u233?nd m\u233? n\u233?ngorayan nden\u233? f\u233?m so gh\u233?ngan enfetat, f\u233?yo tane si waitogh Kerisoene wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?nm\u233?n yau so t\u233?funau k\u233?rt\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?nd m\u233?nde kw\u233?morw\u233?n nden\u233? f\u225? emofem k\u233?rt\u233? efunat a erametat f\u233?m gh\u233?ngan n\u233?fgh\u233?t fiya tanfetangi y\u233?fenjo nj\u233?nafayo.
