Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam emotai f\u233?m s\u225?i em yuwek. W\u233?nde yau eumyotati f\u233?fene yuwek m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i ewifotati f\u233?fene fifioene m\u233?nde. W\u233?nde k\u225?s\u225?fotati f\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?n uw\u233?ghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
