karogh, w\u233?riyam, yaufi t\u233?m\u233?nd, a \u225?mb m\u233? k\u233?s eng\u233?m. Y\u233?ndon ewaw\u233?ngsotan s\u233?nonjo, nden\u233? k\u233?s ewaw\u233?ngsotam\u233?n fronde: emofem ewafrotat y\u233?n\u233? yam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yau so tawaramang\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh.
