ng\u225?r\u225?mng\u225?r\u225?m, a y\u233?ndio awamarogh. K\u233?t\u233? \u225?mb n\u225?k yau y\u233?m \u225?nde noraye nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? yam sem m\u225?m\u225?fi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
F\u225? efe em Yesu Kerisoene t\u233? enamndam\u233?nd k\u233?rot fifi y\u225?njo m\u233?inyotio m\u233?ndef\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram t\u233? y\u233?nmaramai t\u233?fe gh\u233?rs\u233?, y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?ndfem fiya t\u225?itotang\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?nd yau so nawarmbotam o n\u233?kwot nam\u233?indam o nawaramnjam t\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n.
