\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, njam efe terang\u233? yaufiyamam, f\u233?m efe em Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ran so yangotati f\u225? m\u233?tare. W\u233?nde kor f\u233?t\u233?, f\u233?m w\u233?i so em ufoghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
M\u233?rne ersati ndimbal k\u233?rt\u233?, a y\u233?n\u233? ende f\u233?mofem so efalo t\u225?y\u225?tongi Kerisoene n\u225?k. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Njam efe nemna nden\u233? f\u225? y\u233?m \u225?r t\u225?f f\u225? y\u233?n\u233? yau y\u233?m, f\u225? f\u225?yo nawawinde. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
\u193?mbiro\u225?mbiro \u225?r\u233?m so ewaf\u233?nmetat y\u233?fenjo wafroghyam. F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem y\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?n \u225?uw\u233?gh so y\u233?fandat, m\u233?nayofnar f\u225?yo s\u225?i naufotat \u225?mb \u225?rfefaf, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
m\u233?nam\u233?n \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiro \u225?r\u233?m so f\u233?t\u233? ersat y\u233?fenjo k\u233?rt\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Emo njam ewatameta f\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si, f\u233?mofem so ef\u233?nati m\u233?inyotio mer rokar y\u233?maf\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?m f\u233?myo yau nawawindati, emo yau so Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne yaweinde. \u193?rom so y\u233?f\u233?rne n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mo yeite. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Emon njam yeita yanjo fifi m\u233?nde wifogh\u233?t, k\u233?tam\u233? y\u233?n\u233? fifi m\u233?ndeta so t\u233?frarng\u233? k\u233?rt\u233?. Emon njam yeita Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roene m\u233?ndeyan, k\u233?tam\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?rta so t\u233?frarng\u233? tuot akegh gh\u233?rs\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?nd m\u233?nj t\u233? so y\u233?ng\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t meryam wafrogh\u233?t a yau so sak\u233?r y\u233?n\u233?m, efogh so kufarng\u233? wau yuwot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde, \u225?nde y\u233?m t\u233?feyot f\u233?nef\u233?ne, y\u233?ndfem so mer ewafrotam m\u233?inyotio \u225?rfet, y\u233?feyot fifi efe em efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Folene ambinom\u233?n wawanjagh si
