T\u233?fandangi n\u233?m\u233? ndimbale f\u233?r\u233?n y\u233?ndon tafarotan njam y\u233?ndon tafarotan f\u233?fefaf tanjo ng\u225?ngaye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
F\u225? emofem y\u233?ta ew\u225?f\u225?retat m\u233?n\u225?t gh\u233?ngan n\u233?fgh\u233?t m\u233?nde em mer s\u225?i n\u233?retat \u225?mb \u225?rfefaf. F\u225? yau m\u233?nde em s\u225?i ewas\u233?rmbotat m\u233?nam\u233?n Kerisoene wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?nm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u225? f\u233?t\u233? gh\u233?ngan n\u233?f\u233?ghkaf em, w\u233?nde y\u233?mofem yau ewaitotat n\u225?k. F\u225? m\u233?nde em f\u233?m s\u225?i gh\u233?ngan enfetat m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? so nawarsat nden\u233? f\u233?m t\u233? n\u225?myo y\u233?n\u233? fifi yamfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
W\u233?nde tayot, y\u233?nd so nawarsan m\u233?nam\u233?n t\u233?fene Yur\u233? Yesu Kerisoene wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?nm\u233?nro. M\u233?nam\u233?n m\u233?naye y\u225?ne wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?ne mband marat k\u233?r t\u233? t\u233?m tayot, a y\u233?nd t\u233? k\u233?r kw\u233?m mband maratoe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?yotaro m\u233? y\u233?m njam f\u233?m t\u233? gh\u233?ngan enfay\u233?nd o yau, ndimbal yam siy\u233?m nden\u233? f\u233?m t\u233? namndangi tot\u233?r \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Y\u233?feyot emofem ewaitotat y\u233?n\u233? si y\u233?fene gh\u233?rsayan, so y\u233?m krufr\u225?t a gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? y\u233?fefaf w\u233?i m\u233?inyotio Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?rfefaf!
