Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Fol, Keriso Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?r efe y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene m\u233?ndeyan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?ndon y\u233?farotan y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?r\u233?n f\u233?fefaf, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar \u225?rfefaf Efesos k\u233?nj\u250?n, efe em ndimbal mwighaf\u233? Keriso Yesue k\u233?nj\u250?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n t\u233?fene Af\u233? a Yur\u233? Yesu Kerisom so tawaramang\u233? f\u233?fe ng\u225?r\u225?m a krufr\u225?t.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? ewafrote t\u233?feyot mer yam Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Yuyotam Ng\u225?nj\u225?n efe y\u233?m t\u233?fene Yur\u233? Yesu Kerisoene Af\u233?, emo y\u233?n\u233?frendai y\u233?nd m\u233?inyotio njafarm\u233?n mb\u233?rmb\u233?re freng\u233?ghe Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
K\u233?t\u233? frondeyan soram\u233? mband marat yafrotam, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?nmafery\u233?ng Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?nd so y\u233?n\u233?m nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar a t\u233?fnofnar y\u225?ne s\u225?fr\u233?re. M\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?nmuwete, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? mwigh\u233? y\u233?faronam Yesu Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? y\u233?mon so t\u233?ny\u225?tong\u233? y\u225?ne ambum. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u225?itoi y\u225?njo \u225?uw\u233?gh a m\u233?nde. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?ndfem yuyotam Ng\u225?nj\u225?n y\u225?ne ndimbalfifi ng\u225?r\u225?mm\u233?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mon y\u233?nmaramai ram\u233?gh maratae t\u233?fe y\u225?njo \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? Ambum k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Kerisoene f\u233?rke y\u233?nd yuwek y\u233?ny\u225?toi, a w\u233?i t\u233?fene yaufiyam yawalindai y\u233?nam\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ndimbal ng\u225?r\u225?me. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?mon y\u233?nmaramai ndimbal k\u233?r\u225?ye ng\u225?r\u225?m m\u233?inyotio y\u225?njo k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaye a matyame. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yafrotam n\u233?m\u233? y\u225?ne m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n, a saf\u233?t y\u233?kmai t\u233?fefaf kwankwane mwigh\u233? faror\u233?gh y\u233?mon \u225?rk\u233? t\u233? y\u233?kmai wifogh\u233?t Kerisoe k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mwigh\u233? faror\u233?gh so tifong\u233? t\u225?f efogh njam kawerang\u233?. Y\u233?n\u233? efghon y\u233?mon so t\u225?y\u225?tong\u233? \u225?mbiro m\u233?inyotio rokar njafar a mbandan Kerisoene lim\u225?ng\u233?gh mbanmbanan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
M\u233?inyotio yam nufrotat Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mwigh\u233? faror\u233?ghan a m\u233?ndeyan. Kerisoe k\u233?nj\u250?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?nmafery\u233?ng y\u225?njo \u225?rot y\u225?njo m\u233?ndeyan. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mon mwigh\u233? yafrotam k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? r\u233?ny\u233?ghan, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
m\u233?n\u225?t nden\u233? y\u233?nd y\u233?nmorm\u233?n fronde ekmay\u233?m t\u233?fene m\u233?ghm\u233?gh Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n, y\u233?nd m\u233?t\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ndimbal y\u233?tkw\u233?n uyogh\u233?t!
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
A f\u233?m namnday\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?r t\u225?f f\u233?m njam n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd efalo si, mer si \u225?rk\u233? m\u233?n\u225?yam y\u233?n\u233?rse f\u233?feyot wanjar\u233?gh. F\u233?mofem efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd Keriso, a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?kmai y\u225?njo y\u233?ru f\u233?fefaf, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r y\u233?mon \u225?rk\u233? t\u233? uny\u233?ghofnar norayai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?ndfem so tawanang\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? uny\u233?ghofnar si emndai y\u225?njo \u225?r, a y\u233?n\u233? yam y\u233?nd y\u233?ny\u225?tote efalo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so t\u233?ramang\u233? m\u233?inyoe yuwek k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?feyot efe em y\u225?ne. Y\u233?ndfem so yuyotam y\u225?ne ndimbal y\u233?tkw\u233?n!
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Fol Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayet efalo y\u225?togh \u225?rfenem\u233?n Efesos k\u233?nj\u250?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan, k\u233?t\u225?ndmayo y\u233?nd n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?n f\u233?fene ndimbal mwigham\u233?n Yur\u233? Yesue k\u233?nj\u250?n a f\u233?fene uw\u233?ghm\u233?n m\u233?inyotio Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?r\u233?t, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
y\u233?ndo t\u250?m\u233?n k\u225?njo tarametan Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne f\u233?fenem\u233?n. Njam y\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? koraiw\u233?m, y\u233?ndo t\u250?m\u233?n yamnendan f\u233?fe w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
t\u233?fene Yur\u233? Yesu Kerisoene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, minde ndimbal Af\u233?, s\u225?i tawaramang\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r f\u233?fe. Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram so t\u225?y\u225?tong\u233? f\u233?m k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaf\u233? a safot t\u233?kmang\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n f\u233?fefaf, m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?mofem mat so tiy\u225?tongi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Y\u233?ndon n\u243?mnendan m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?fene mwigh\u233? so k\u225?s\u225?w\u233?rngi, m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m so mat em n\u233?m\u233? m\u233?ghm\u233?gh y\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n f\u233?m k\u233?s emotai, nder\u233? mer freng\u233?gh y\u233?m y\u233?mo uny\u233?ghofnar si k\u233?s norayai y\u225?njo \u225?rfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
F\u233?m w\u233?i so mat em nder\u233? minde ndimbal y\u233?m y\u225?ne waft\u233? \u225?s\u225?foghan t\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n efe efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r y\u233?n\u233?m. Y\u233?n\u233? waft\u233? sn\u225?s\u225?fote t\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n siy\u233?m nden\u233?m\u233?nayo waft\u233? k\u233?r ro muy\u233? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
\u225?rk\u233?m\u233?naye Keriso yanoi k\u233?rta a yumnjoi f\u225? y\u225?njo tamb\u233?n ng\u225?ngata njafar lim\u225?n\u233?ghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
K\u233?t\u233?, Kerisom elimnde m\u233?inyotio njafarm\u233?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r, si muy\u233?, waft\u233?, a yur\u233?. Y\u225?faf y\u233?m minde tuk\u233?n y\u233?tkw\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? m\u233?inyotio tuk\u233?n waftaf\u233? y\u233?tkw\u233?nta y\u233?n\u233? mband maratan a w\u233?i soram\u233? mband marat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
