m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m, m\u233?rne y\u233?maf\u233? m\u233?inyotio Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?rf\u233?, so em waftaf\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t mat so k\u225?y\u225?tongi nder\u233? marat a tomb\u233?, nder\u233? tuk a k\u233?njkam, y\u233?m Kerisoene uw\u233?gh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?nd yau so mat kamndang\u233?m y\u225?ne uw\u233?gh m\u233?inyoe. W\u233?nde y\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? noraiwam f\u233?m so f\u233?t\u233? mat kamndangi Kerisoene uw\u233?gh, a y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m so tawafong\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n m\u233?inyotio Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene afoghkaf k\u233?nj\u250?t.
