Yuwan aem t\u250?m\u233?n, mer, a m\u233?tar. F\u233?fenjo uw\u233?gh euyafotati m\u233?naye awarny\u233?ghe \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiro \u225?rf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
