N\u233?m\u233? y\u225?ne fifi y\u233?m, "f\u225? n\u233?nguyoi tuk\u233?t"? Y\u225?ne fifi nden\u233? y\u233?m f\u225? fronde n\u233?newory\u233?ng mband maratot minde yuwot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?yo f\u225? efe t\u233? n\u233?newory\u233?ng f\u225?yo y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m efe nuyoi tuk\u233?t, minde tuk\u233?t a engwaindai m\u233?inyotio njafar tuk, m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?mon so tafarng\u233? m\u233?inyotio mband marat yandio. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u225? y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m emon "ewaramete tamb\u233?n \u225?r\u233?t," ekafetam \u225?mb Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?r, \u225?mb m\u233?n\u225?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r, \u225?mb marataye si afrogh \u225?r, \u225?mb misi a watamegh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?mon m\u233?inyotio Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?r efrendam Ng\u225?nj\u225?njene \u225?s\u225?fogh wafrogh\u233?t, m\u233?n\u225?t Kerisoene fifi s\u225?i y\u233?rametat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?nd m\u233?inyotio so kamndang\u233?m \u225?mbiro ndimbal mwigh\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?n a matyaman Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene Ambumoenem\u233?n. Y\u233?nd so kamndang\u233?m anoghkaf \u225?r. Y\u233?nd so f\u233?yotaro y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene m\u233?nde ndern\u225?ye y\u233?m t\u233?feyot s\u225?i y\u233?m, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Keriso f\u225?yo k\u233?s y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?nd yau so y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r. Y\u233?nd yau s\u225?i s\u243?fam y\u233?n\u233?rsa a mbormboram y\u233?ng\u233?rsa y\u233?n\u233? warsogh k\u233?r ro \u225?rfene watameghan, emofem elimndat \u225?mb \u225?r k\u233?rtat y\u233?fenjo wafroghm\u233?n uny\u233?ghe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
W\u233?ndende, y\u233?nd efalo s\u225?i norayam uw\u233?gh mb\u233?rmb\u233?re, y\u233?nd t\u225?f so nanotam Kerisoefaf m\u233?inyotio yaman, efe y\u233?m s\u233?nko. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Nden\u233? fifioene s\u233?nko, y\u233?mo y\u225?ut\u225?ne m\u233?inyotio fifi m\u233?n\u225?t so nanote merk\u233?raye. \u193?mb fifikafe eurau \u225?mb fifikafefaf m\u233?n\u225?t m\u233?inyotio fifi so y\u233?m muyaf\u233?. Njam f\u233?nataf\u233?nat\u233? kafekafeyam y\u233?fenjo mer \u225?s\u225?fogh ewafrotat, y\u233?nd so n\u225?uw\u233?tam \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiro k\u233?nj\u250?n mindefifi ndimbalk\u233?r\u225?ye.
