F\u233?m t\u233? t\u225?f kw\u233?fkw\u233?fan tamorw\u233?n, w\u233?nde f\u233?m t\u233? namndangi Yurane \u225?r, f\u233?m sem kwayaghayan. Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m so f\u233?t\u233? emor nden\u233? kwayaghane ambum. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Kwayaghane mbwe sem m\u233?inyotio mer yam, mbark\u225?nd yam, a efalo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Mato t\u233?ronjangi Yur\u233? \u225?rk\u233? yaman n\u225?uwete. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
N\u233?mndafi yau ewafrotati kw\u233?fkw\u233?foene mbwefnar yam, w\u233?nde ekmetati kwayaghat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
W\u225?iw\u225?iaf\u233? y\u233?m s\u225?i norayat m\u233?nam\u233?n n\u233?m\u233? \u225?y\u225?r\u233?ghofnar \u225?r\u233?m ewafrotat kwankwane. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
W\u233?nde m\u233?inyotio yam njam k\u233?nakmangi kwayaghan, m\u233?inyotio yam k\u233?namndangi saf\u233?n, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
m\u233?nam\u233?n kwayaghayam eufane m\u233?inyotio yam. Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? si noraye,
