Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde, kor so f\u233?t\u233? em m\u233?nam\u233?n ndern\u225?ye f\u233?m emor. Yau emor ndenanit k\u225?fetafnar \u225?rnit, w\u233?nde k\u225?fet\u233? \u225?rnit. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Ewafrotati merk\u233?r\u225?ye m\u233?inyotio \u225?s\u225?fogh f\u233?fene k\u233?s em, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? sem yaufi efogh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Yau aem fifiofnar, f\u233?t\u233? so mat n\u225?y\u225?totati Yurane m\u233?nde n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m f\u233?fe wafrogh\u233?t.
