Yau w\u233?ri nu enetati w\u233?riot, y\u233?n\u233? yamam f\u233?m so ewas\u233?rmbote, w\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram atawafong\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Norayati f\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?n samse, wafnjagh waghe, a mb\u233?rmb\u233?re waghe. Wafnjagh wagh a sams wagh erametati Yurafaf \u225?uw\u233?gh tikfe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
T\u233?fene Yur\u233? Yesu Kerisoene y\u233?tkw\u233?nan, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Afai t\u250?m\u233?n k\u225?njo yarametati m\u233?inyotio yamm\u233?n.
