Amaf, n\u225?y\u225?retati f\u233?m f\u233?fenjo \u225?rfefaf nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yurafaf k\u233?s n\u225?y\u225?retati. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?njar siy\u233?m s\u233?nko yatnoefaf nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Keriso siy\u233?m s\u233?nko Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?nfaf, a Keriso siy\u233?m f\u225?yo Yesuene m\u233?rnoene Wanjar\u233?gh \u225?r y\u233?m, y\u225?ne fifi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?s f\u225?yo n\u225?y\u225?rete Kerisoefaf, so f\u233?t\u233? amaf f\u225?yo n\u225?y\u225?retat y\u233?fenjarfefaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
\u193?r, euwetati f\u233?fetnof, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Kerisom yuwetam Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n a y\u233?ramai y\u225?njo gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u225?yot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Yesum yafrotam y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t yiy\u225?toi Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar. Y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?morm\u233?n ndenanit y\u233?mo kar y\u233?nd y\u233?nmumbary\u233?ng nue, njam y\u233?mo y\u233?n\u233?rsam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si t\u233?fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Y\u233?mo yafrote y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n y\u233?nmanai y\u225?njo s\u225?fr\u233?re sariaf\u233? a nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar a t\u233?fnofnar, mborofnar o \u225?mb f\u233?r\u233?ngf\u233?rngofnar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
\u193?r\u233?m so f\u233?t\u233? euwetat y\u233?fetnof nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? k\u233?s euwetat y\u233?fenjo fifi. \u193?r emon yuwete y\u225?t\u233?n n\u225?uwete f\u225?yo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Emon yau so m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat y\u233?fande y\u225?njo fifi. W\u233?nde y\u233?ndfem emanjnam a ewarawenam, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Kerisom ndern\u225?ye yafrote Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
m\u233?nam\u233?n Kerisoene fifi kafe y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Nden\u233? Buk si noraye, "Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan \u225?rom so t\u233?frangong\u233? y\u225?ref\u233? a y\u225?tm\u233? a y\u225?tnof\u233? \u225?mbiro k\u225?y\u225?tend, a s\u243?mbio so kamndend \u225?mbiro." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
K\u233?t\u233? y\u233?m k\u233?njkame kwankwane efalo yam y\u233?n\u233? Buk sian yufane saf\u233?t, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd norayan Kerisoenem\u233?n a Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?nm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
