Faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, ey\u225?retati f\u233?fenjo mbandm\u233?n yur\u233? utman\u233?ghaf\u233? a f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233?, utman\u233?gh tikfe yafrotati nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? ndern\u225?ye f\u233?mon Keriso so yiy\u225?rete. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Yau ewafrotati y\u233?n\u233? t\u225?fandro njam y\u233?mofem efandat, m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m m\u233?nde em y\u233?mofem s\u225?i efalo ey\u225?totat, w\u233?nde m\u233?inyotio tikfe f\u233?mofem t\u225?f ewafrotati n\u233?mat Ng\u225?nj\u225?n m\u233?nde y\u233?m, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Kerisoene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Ewafrotati f\u233?fenjo \u225?s\u225?fogh nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233?, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?mofem Yurane \u225?s\u225?fogh yafrotati, yau \u225?rfene. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
