a nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?fene sandol afreng\u233?ghkaf so em m\u233?n\u225?t krufrat mer si waitogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
T\u250?m\u233?n efghon ersati ndimbal mwigh\u233? nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? awamb\u233?gh mbakw, y\u233?naye f\u233?m so f\u233?yotaro em yaufi \u225?roene m\u233?inyotio f\u233?saf\u233? fimb. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Tawanangi wanjar\u233?gh nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? asm\u233?gh walaf, a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roene witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? n\u225?if\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Yafrotati m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh k\u233?nj\u250?n n\u243?mnendati Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene w\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh\u233?t. Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayati m\u233?inyotio yaman Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roene lim\u225?n\u233?ghan. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan mwigh\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? aem a yau k\u233?kmbongi m\u233?inyotio Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?r\u233?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayati. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayati w\u233?i tayot, m\u233?n\u225?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so kwaramang\u233? si t\u225?f njam y\u233?nd afreng\u233?ghkaf w\u233?m siyot, a m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?nd so norayan f\u233?rf\u233?rofnar a s\u225?i mat ey\u225?totan mer siyoene kwankwane yam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?nd w\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam m\u233?n\u225?t so tawaufrotaw\u233?n \u225?r\u233?t mer si y\u225?nem\u233?n. A y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan y\u233?nd s\u233?nonjo kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngon w\u233?lau. Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayati m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?nd f\u233?rf\u233?rofnar so mer si nafrotan nden\u233? y\u233?ndon so f\u233?t\u233?.
