Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde, \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? f\u250?tar\u233?f, nden\u233? f\u233?m t\u250?m\u233?n k\u225?y\u225?retaw\u233?t tafaf njam y\u233?nd kw\u233?morw\u233?n f\u233?fefaf, minde mer y\u233?m nden\u233? f\u233?m n\u225?y\u225?retati tafaf s\u233?nonjo njamandio y\u233?nd w\u233?m nayu f\u233?feta. M\u233? n\u233?ng\u225?s\u225?fotati f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? a ngerngeraf\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t so tifongi f\u233?fenjo wanjar\u233?gh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
