Ewafrotati m\u233?inyotio yam \u225?w\u225?taran\u233?ghofnar o amror\u233?ghofnar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?yo f\u233?m so em k\u233?rtafnar a nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene f\u233?w\u233?nf\u233?w\u233?nofnar ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r, efe emor y\u233?n\u233? wasneng\u233?gh mband maratan a yaufi \u225?r. F\u233?m t\u225?f natremngotati y\u233?fefaf ndenanit k\u233?nd nanetat njafaran. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Naweretati taikrataye k\u233?t\u225?n gh\u233?rs\u233? sifaf. Njam f\u233?mofem ewafrotati, y\u233?nd so minde \u225?uw\u233?ghan w\u233?m f\u233?fenem\u233?n Kerisoene angogh efghon, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? yam so yuyafote nden\u233? m\u233?inyotio tane \u225?s\u225?fogh f\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n yau so y\u233?m fifiofnar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
W\u233?nde Y\u233?nd so n\u225?uwetan njam y\u233?ndo gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?tarnan, nasuna ndenanit gh\u233?ng\u233?n ram\u233?gh w\u233?kw\u233?r Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?fene ndimbal mwigh\u233? k\u233?r ro \u225?s\u225?foghm\u233?n y\u233?m ram\u233?gh Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
A f\u233?m fiya k\u225?uwetangi y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n a n\u225?uwetam y\u233?ndf\u233?.
