\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?nd m\u233?ghm\u233?ghan w\u233?m Yur\u233? Yesuene k\u233?nj\u250?n s\u225?i yaf\u225?retan Timoti k\u233?t\u225?n f\u233?fefaf w\u233?keye, nden\u233? tayot w\u233?i so y\u233?m waw\u233?ngsogh njam f\u225? n\u233?nangota a kwaufrong\u233? f\u233?fenem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Tane \u225?mb \u225?r yau y\u233?m nden\u233? Timoti k\u233?s y\u233?m, emo efalofifi ewarawene f\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
M\u233?inyotio \u225?mb \u225?r n\u233?retat m\u233? y\u233?fenjo m\u233?ndefaf\u233?tro, yau Yesu Kerisoene m\u233?ndefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
W\u233?nde f\u233?m mat em nden\u233? Timoti t\u233? kauyafote f\u225?yo. Ndenanit y\u225?refaf\u233? y\u233?nau ambumof\u233? n\u225?s\u225?fot, y\u233?nd t\u233? k\u225?s\u225?fowam mer sian. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Y\u233?nd m\u233?ghm\u233?ghan w\u233?m s\u225?i y\u233?ngw\u225?f\u225?retan Timoti f\u233?fefaf w\u233?keye. W\u233?nde fronde, y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? so nufrote tafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Y\u233?ndo efalo yiy\u225?totan Yur\u233? nden\u233? y\u233?nd y\u233?ndio so w\u233?n\u233?m w\u233?keye f\u233?fefaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Y\u233?nd nemnan y\u233?ndo t\u225?f so y\u233?ngw\u225?faretan Efafroditus s\u225?i n\u233?ngangota f\u233?fefaf. F\u225? y\u233?m efalo f\u250?tar Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n. Y\u233?ndf\u233? t\u233? k\u225?s\u225?fowam m\u233?n\u225?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?neyot \u225?s\u225?fogh tafrowam m\u233?rne. Y\u233?nd k\u225?s\u225?fowam minde, ndenanit fiyar\u233? k\u233?s em. Njam y\u233?nd m\u233?nde kw\u233?m w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t, f\u233?mofem t\u233? t\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retati tafaf. Y\u233?mo t\u233? kw\u225?ut\u225?ne f\u233?fene t\u233?fnan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? m\u233?nde y\u233?m mindefifi m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tawinjong\u233? m\u233?inyotio f\u233?m, f\u225? siy\u233?m mwighayam yaw\u233?rsote m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd nden\u233? f\u225? enjne t\u233?morw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
N\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t, f\u225? enjne t\u233?morw\u233?n, a kaka krotro, w\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?n gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? y\u233?morm\u233?n y\u225?faf a y\u233?nd w\u233?i, m\u233?n\u225?t tafaf yau so y\u233?m minde gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m mindefifi m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i y\u233?ngw\u225?f\u225?retan f\u225? k\u233?t\u225?n f\u233?fefaf m\u233?n\u225?t njam f\u233?mofem tinjongi t\u225?f f\u233?m so \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? em, a y\u233?nd yau so waw\u233?rsote mwighayam f\u233?fenem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Tumyongi f\u225? Yurane k\u233?nj\u250?n mindefifi \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? a taramangi utman\u233?gh nden\u233? \u225?roe f\u225? siy\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? k\u233?r kaka y\u233?morm\u233?n Kerisoene \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fnan, m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i kwaramang\u233? ta w\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mofem yau so w\u225?ut\u225?nati ta.
