\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Efalofifi mbark\u225?nd \u225?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Ambinom\u233?n, tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, n\u225?uwetati Yurane k\u233?nj\u250?n! Y\u233?nayam yau mwighat wawinde ta m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?farotan nden\u233?yameyo yamm\u233?n f\u233?fefaf y\u233?ndon k\u233?s y\u233?farotam\u233?n fronde, efaloe, y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m f\u233?fenjoyo merot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Kor aem y\u233?fefaf emofem ewafrotat yaufi, efe ndenanit em \u225?gh\u233?, efe norayat m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i enfetat gh\u233?ngan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m efalo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?r. A yau y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m m\u233?nam\u233?n \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?m kar gh\u233?ngan t\u233?n\u233?nfetaw\u233?t. Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?nlimnde m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i y\u225?wefnotam Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne. Y\u233?ndfem k\u225?njo yarametam Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne m\u233?nam\u233?n n\u233?m\u233? Keriso Yesum t\u233? yafrotam t\u233?feyot. Y\u233?nd yau nemnam t\u233?fene fifi n\u233?f\u233?gh\u233?t siy\u233?m ndimbalfifi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Njam fifioene yam y\u233?m ndimbalfifi, f\u233?yo y\u233?nd t\u225?f so korayang\u233?n y\u233?nd w\u233?mor merk\u233?r\u225?ye. Y\u233?nd njam kw\u233?morw\u233?n \u225?mb \u225?r emofem mwigh\u233? taikre y\u233?rsat fifioene yamta, y\u233?ndo so tawaindang\u233?n m\u233?inyotio f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Y\u233?nd gh\u233?ngan w\u233?nfay\u233?nd njam y\u233?nd 8 efogh namnday\u233?n, a y\u233?nd k\u233?tamam\u233?n w\u233?m Israil yum\u233?n a Benjaminene m\u233?r\u233?nm\u233?n a y\u233?nd w\u233?m efalofifi Ibru \u225?r. Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Farasi \u225?r, y\u233?ndon kor merk\u233?r\u225?ye ewaitotam\u233?n Mosesene n\u225?k. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
A y\u233?nd m\u233?nde kw\u233?morw\u233?n nden\u233? y\u233?ndon tas\u233?rmbotaw\u233?n Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n. Y\u233?ndon tawafrotaw\u233?n m\u233?inyotio ndern\u225?ye n\u225?k t\u233?morw\u233?n, y\u233?nd kw\u233?morw\u233?n t\u233?fnofnar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?inyotio yam tamorw\u233?n ndimbalfifi tayot, w\u233?nde s\u233?nonjo y\u233?ndon efandan fifiofnar m\u233?nam\u233?n Kerisoene t\u233?fnan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Yau y\u233?n\u233? yamro, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m nden\u233? efalo yiy\u225?totan tane Yur\u233? Yesu Keriso siy\u233?m ndimbalfifi, f\u233?yo y\u233?ndo efandan m\u233?inyotio \u225?mb rokar fifiofnar. Y\u233?ndo efalo yiy\u225?totan Yesu, f\u233?yo y\u233?ndon t\u233? tatarnan m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? rokar. Y\u233?ndon y\u233?n\u233? tafandan m\u233?rm\u233?rnit a taikrataye kawaretan Yesu Kerisoefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?nd s\u225?i w\u233?m y\u225?ne, s\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd mbark\u225?nd y\u233?nre Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233?, yau m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndon tanwaitotan n\u225?k, w\u233?nde m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndon efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?n Keriso. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233?ny\u225?tong\u233? mbark\u225?nd y\u233?maf\u233? ndimbal mwighaye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
M\u233?inyotio y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t mat so k\u225?y\u225?ton Keriso a s\u225?i t\u233?rnon anogh waft\u233?, a s\u225?i wafnyang y\u225?ne t\u233?kr\u225?tan a kamndan nden\u233? f\u225? y\u225?ne k\u233?ran, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?ghm\u233?ghan y\u233?nd y\u233?ndio so kanon k\u233?tam\u233? k\u233?rta.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 M\u233?njt\u233? ay\u233?ng\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n fai r\u233?saghfaf
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?nd yau namndetan nden\u233? y\u233?ndon t\u233? eyanjang\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? yam o t\u233? n\u233?namndan f\u233?w\u233?nf\u233?w\u233?nofnar. Y\u233?nd m\u233? nawarafnan waing\u233?gh\u233?t m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tanan fai \u225?rk\u233? Keriso Yesum t\u233? wiy\u225?toi y\u233?nd yandio. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, y\u233?nd yau nemnan nden\u233? y\u233?ndo t\u233? yanan, w\u233?nde \u225?mbiro yam y\u233?ndon yafrotan siy\u233?m s\u225?i kwawalindang\u233? n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m tane s\u233?mta a y\u233?nd nufotan m\u233?n\u225?t tiy\u225?njang\u233?n n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m fronde. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?nd n\u233?rsan mbark\u225?nde yafarenan yatogh m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i kawaindang\u233?n fai r\u233?sagh\u233?t, \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u225?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? wanmoi y\u233?nd Keriso Yesue k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?n\u233? gh\u233?rsat y\u233?maf\u233? njafaran.
