M\u233?inyotio efe y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m mb\u233?rmb\u233?re anoghkaf fai kemnang\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? ende w\u233?i. A njam f\u233?mofem nemnati f\u233?natayero y\u233?n\u233? yamm\u233?n, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so ekmete saf\u233?n f\u233?feyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?ndfem fiya m\u233? t\u225?itotang\u233?m efalo si \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?njam t\u233? y\u233?nmaramai.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, m\u233?inyotio f\u233?m fiya kuwaitotangi tane wafrogh yamam\u233?, a merk\u233?raye efandati \u225?mb \u225?r efe tamorang\u233?rw\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? ende y\u233?ndfem ewaufarotam f\u233?fe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Y\u233?ndon tawaufrotan f\u233?fe y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n t\u225?rf\u225?r mbinotm\u233? fronde, a s\u233?nonjo y\u233?ndon y\u233?f\u233?rtan yengamaf\u233?: y\u233?na em t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r emorang nden\u233? m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?rnit Kerisoene wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?nfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
K\u233?t\u225?n wifoghfaf, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so ewirone f\u225?, y\u233?mofem ewafrotat y\u233?fene fifioene m\u233?nde n\u233?mat em, f\u225? em tuktuk m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?fene w\u225?iw\u225?iaf\u233? wafroghyamm\u233?n, a f\u225? nemnat m\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n mbandm\u233?n rokarm\u233?nro. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
