M\u233?naye y\u225?ne waftaye s\u225?i elimnda m\u233?inyotio yam, y\u233?mon so tawengong\u233? t\u233?fene njang\u233?n fifi a t\u225?y\u225?tong\u233? nden\u233? y\u225?njoyo minde mer fifi.
