A y\u233?ndon emotang\u233?n f\u233?m, tane ndimbal mwighaf\u233? f\u250?tar, m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i ew\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? s\u243?mbio amaf, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?maf\u233? k\u225?s\u225?fotam y\u233?ndf\u233? mer si k\u233?nj\u250?n, m\u233?rne y\u233?maf\u233? Klement a \u225?mb \u225?r emof\u233? k\u225?s\u225?fotaw\u233?m y\u233?ndf\u233?, endefene y\u233?tkw\u233?n ekai k\u233?t\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? bukan.
