Yau mwighayam ewaw\u233?rsotat rokarm\u233?n, w\u233?nde m\u233?inyotio f\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?ghan yamnendati Ng\u225?nj\u225?n n\u233?mat f\u233?m m\u233?nde em, t\u250?m\u233?n yamnendati f\u225? k\u225?njo tikfe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
A Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene krufr\u225?tam, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m minde tuk\u233?n y\u233?m \u225?rfene matyamta, so ewarawene f\u233?fene tik\u233?f a mwigh\u233? Keriso Yesuene k\u233?nj\u250?n.
