M\u233? ekmetati wafroghyaman m\u233?inyotio f\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? kotametati a tarsati y\u233?nam\u233? ta tamb\u233?n, tane sian a tane wafroghyaman. F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam emo y\u233?nmaramete t\u233?fe krufr\u225?t so y\u233?m f\u233?fefaf.
