Y\u233?nd yau norayan m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd n\u225?ronjan. Y\u233?nd t\u233? notametam\u233?n remngogh\u233?t y\u233?nayan n\u233?m\u233? tane wam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
\u193?nde yau em rokar, y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m y\u233?n\u233?m\u233?n. \u193?nde em t\u225?rf\u225?r rokar, y\u233?nd w\u233?i mat w\u233?m y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n. Y\u233?nd t\u233? notametam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? kwankwane yam, m\u233?n\u225?t m\u233?inyotio sifayan, \u225?rk\u233? efghon, y\u233?nd w\u233?m f\u233?yotaro, t\u233?u w\u233?m suaf\u233? o siogh, s\u225?i wam t\u225?rf\u225?r o nambioro. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
