Y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?nayo mer si \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?nmorm\u233?n f\u233?fefaf t\u233? y\u233?ng\u233?m m\u233?inyotio mband maratam\u233?, a mbwe n\u233?ngafote m\u233?inyotio sifayam\u233? engwengote \u225?rfene gh\u233?rs\u233?, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? tawengote f\u233?fene gh\u233?rs\u233? k\u233?tam\u233? y\u233?n\u233? efoghta njam n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd fronde a mat namnday\u233?nd efaloe Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ng\u225?r\u225?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
