Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan, k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? y\u233?n\u233? efogh y\u233?nd njam n\u225?y\u225?reyay\u233?m f\u233?fenem\u233?n, y\u233?nd yau n\u233?kmbeyay\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh f\u233?fenem\u233?n. T\u250?m\u233?n tamneng\u233?w\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tawafotau y\u225?ne m\u233?ndeyoene matyame a Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram so ewaramete k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233? a mat y\u225?togh yam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
A y\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayam m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m so emor nden\u233? Yur\u233? m\u233?nde k\u233?s y\u233?m a so y\u233?remngote m\u233?inyotio yaman. F\u233?mofem efunati mbwe m\u233?n\u225?yan m\u233?inyotio meryam wafroghan, a nanotati Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene matyaman. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
A y\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? w\u233?i norayam nden\u233? muy\u233? ram\u233?ghkaf so em Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene m\u233?inyotio ndimbal waftaye m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?fefaf so y\u233?m ndimbal awamarogh a m\u233?tar, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
a k\u225?njo ram\u233?gh \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? Afai. F\u225? f\u225?yo t\u233? efalo ey\u225?toi s\u225?i tawanangi m\u233?inyotio rokar n\u233?m\u233? ew\u225?frendam y\u225?njo nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar \u225?r\u233?t efe emor kwayaghane lim\u225?n\u233?ghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Y\u233?mon t\u233? y\u233?nmanjary\u233?ng y\u233?nd k\u233?tam\u233? kw\u233?fitane lim\u225?n\u233?ghta a y\u233?nmufary\u233?ng y\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n Ambumoene lim\u225?n\u233?gh k\u233?nj\u250?t y\u233?mon efe yuwetam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u225?ne Ambumoene \u225?s\u225?fogh k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?nmanjary\u233?ng a ewaindai t\u233?fene yaufi.
