Ambum siy\u233?m mbanmban y\u233?m fandaghofnar Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene, fronde-s\u233?nko m\u233?inyotio ufroghm\u233?n rokarta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Y\u225?ne k\u233?nj\u250?nro Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam m\u233?inyotio rokar tawafrotau: rokar njafaran a mbandan, fandaghm\u233?n a fandaghofnar, n\u233?m\u233? t\u233?u lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? o waftaf\u233? \u225?r o lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r o si muy\u233? \u225?r. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam m\u233?inyotio rokar tawafrotau y\u225?ne Ambum k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? a m\u233? y\u225?ne Ambumotro. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Keriso siy\u233?m frondeyo y\u233?m m\u233?inyotio rokar sem soram\u233?, a m\u233? y\u225?ne k\u233?nj\u250?nro m\u233?inyotio rokar naweretat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
A Keriso siy\u233?m Yesuene m\u233?rnoene s\u233?nko, y\u225?ne fifi. F\u225? w\u233?ikor siy\u233?m r\u233?ny\u233?gh a fronde-s\u233?nko efe t\u233? nanoi k\u233?tam\u233? k\u233?rta, m\u233?n\u225?t m\u233?inyotio rokaran f\u225?ro so y\u233?m fronde sifayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n m\u233?inyotio y\u225?ne afoghkaf s\u225?i t\u233?morw\u233?n Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
A y\u225?ne k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam s\u225?i tanwangongai yandro m\u233?inyotio rokar, n\u233?m\u233? rokar em mbandan o njafaran. Yesu k\u233?r y\u233?morw\u233?n wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?nan a nertam y\u225?ne f\u233?r\u233?k y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? y\u233?mo yafrotam krufr\u225?t yam.
