T\u225?nd\u225?i f\u233?m nayu t\u233? tamorw\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?neta a m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?fenjo mwigham\u233?n a f\u233?fenjo yaufi wafroghyamm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
W\u233?nde s\u233?nonjo y\u233?mon t\u233? ey\u225?toi f\u233?m y\u225?njo f\u250?tar m\u233?naye Kerisoene fifie k\u233?r k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i t\u225?y\u225?tong\u233? nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene s\u225?fr\u233?re, f\u233?w\u233?nf\u233?w\u233?nofnar a t\u233?fnofnar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
F\u233?yo f\u233?m t\u225?f m\u233?njt\u233? em ndimbal mwighayan a taikrataye ewakai. Yau n\u225?s\u225?mbnetati f\u233?fene m\u233?ghm\u233?ghta \u225?nde naweray\u233?nd mer sian. Y\u233?n\u233? mer si fiy\u233?m f\u233?mofem \u225?rk\u233? t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd a \u225?rk\u233? t\u233? t\u233?ngwaitotaw\u233?t m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?t mband maratan, a \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?naye y\u233?nd, Fol, n\u233?n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?n faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r.
