Y\u233?nd n\u225?uwetan tane t\u233?kr\u225?tm\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?fe w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t, tane fifie t\u233?krat k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? y\u233?ndo ew\u225?ut\u225?nan wifogh\u233?t n\u233?m\u233? m\u233? y\u233?m Kerisoene t\u233?krat y\u225?ne fifi, Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n t\u233?fnan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam w\u233?kafai y\u233?nd s\u225?i k\u233?namndangay\u233?n y\u225?ne faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t Yesuene m\u233?rnot. Tane \u225?s\u225?fogh siy\u233?m s\u225?i ewatametan f\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si afoghare. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
T\u225?nd\u225?i Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?n\u233? si y\u233?tnoi kwankwane m\u233?inyotio fronde \u225?r satata, w\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? si s\u233?nonjo saur\u233?ghkaf y\u233?m Yurane \u225?rfefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mwigh\u233? faror\u233?gh siy\u233?m s\u225?i mat ey\u225?tota y\u225?njo kwankwane yam y\u225?njo \u225?r\u233?t, y\u233?n\u233? wem\u225?r a minde ndimbal kwankwane yam \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m y\u225?ne m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?t. A kwankwane yam siy\u233?m nden\u233? Keriso siy\u233?m f\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n. A y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan, f\u233?m mat em nden\u233? f\u233?m so emor Ng\u225?nj\u225?njaf\u233? njafaran \u225?mb kaye.
