Y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m f\u233?m s\u225?i mat em nder\u233? ndimbal k\u233?r\u225?ye n\u225?smetan f\u233?feyot a f\u225? Laodikia yuwon efe em, a m\u233?inyotio y\u233?feyot emofem yau y\u233?fandat tane s\u225?f. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Tane m\u233?nde siy\u233?m f\u225? s\u225?i em waw\u233?ngsoghkaf tikfan a \u225?mbiro uw\u233?ghan, f\u233?yo f\u225? so em afoghare wem\u225?r \u225?rk\u233? efalo matyamam y\u233?n\u233?rse. Y\u233?n\u233? ende f\u225? so mat em Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene kwankwane yam, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m Keriso f\u225?yo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u225? siy\u233?m ki emo esaune m\u233?inyotio t\u233?noghm\u233?n ngonj\u233?l Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233? a matyam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t emo yau so ewasote. Y\u233?mofem t\u233?u ewatametat y\u233?n\u233? mwigh\u233? \u225?rk\u233? mernit n\u233?retat, w\u233?nde yau ey\u225?retati f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Ndemam\u233?n y\u233?nd yuk\u233?r w\u233?m f\u233?fefaf fifie, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd f\u233?maf\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m mb\u233?rmb\u233?re. A n\u225?uwetan njam y\u233?ndon efandan ndern\u225?ye f\u233?m so \u225?mbiro f\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?n watameghan em a nder\u233? muyaf\u233? f\u233?fene ndimbal mwigh\u233? y\u233?m Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n.
