F\u233?mofem t\u233? yanay\u233?nd Keriso Yesu nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yur\u233?. Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde, m\u233?njtaye aemor y\u225?ne k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
S\u233?r\u233?mb y\u233?ghkaf aem a erametati f\u233?fenjo gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u225?ne k\u233?nj\u250?n, muy\u233? r\u233?sagh ndimbal mwighayan ndern\u225?ye f\u233?m t\u233? enwatametam\u233?n, a t\u250?m\u233?n aem k\u225?njo ram\u233?gh \u225?r.
