M\u233?inyotio Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene afoghare yam y\u233?m Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n, y\u225?ne fifiyan {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
a Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n f\u233?m t\u233? ewanay\u233?ng k\u233?t\u225?n wafogh gh\u233?rsafaf. Keriso siy\u233?m s\u233?nko m\u233?inyotio waftaf\u233? \u225?r a si muy\u233? \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Kerisoene k\u233?nj\u250?n f\u233?m t\u233? enfay\u233?nd gh\u233?ngan, yau y\u233?n\u233? gh\u233?ngan n\u233?fghe syafrotam\u233?nd \u225?r\u233?m, w\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? gh\u233?ngan n\u233?fghe syafrotam Kerisom, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m yuwekot k\u233?tam\u233? y\u233?n\u233? yaufiyamoene waftata. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Njam f\u233?m ewalitotam\u233?nd, f\u233?m t\u233? eyatotam\u233?nd Kerisof\u233?, a walitogh k\u233?nj\u250?n f\u233?m w\u233?i t\u233? nanoy\u233?nd Kerisof\u233? f\u233?fenjo ndimbal mwigh\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene waftayan, emo yanoi k\u233?rta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Njam f\u233?m k\u233?rw\u233?n tamorw\u233?n f\u233?fenjo yaufiyam k\u233?nj\u250?n a gh\u233?ngan n\u233?fghofnar f\u233?fenjo fifiyan, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam gh\u233?rsaf\u233? ey\u225?toi m\u233?rne Kerisof\u233?. Ng\u225?nj\u225?n yawalindai t\u233?fene m\u233?inyotio yaufiyam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?mo yit\u233?rmboi t\u233?fene yaufiyamm\u233?n f\u233?r\u233?n a y\u233?namndam wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?nan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
A wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?nan Kerisom engwayai waft\u233? mb\u233?rmb\u233?re lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?rta a si muy\u233? \u225?rta. F\u225? nauyafoi kwayaghaye nden\u233? y\u233?mo m\u233?inyotio t\u233? ewainday\u233?ng. S\u233?nonjo m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m t\u233? efandat nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?rafefaf yau y\u233?m waft\u233?.
