Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde emo yau t\u225?f n\u225?k ewafrota m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mofem n\u233?m\u233? enetati njamke o nu, o nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar efoghm\u233?n o tot\u233?r gh\u233?rare t\u233?m\u233?ndm\u233?n o Safatm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? yam em mbanmbanro k\u233?t\u225?n efalo n\u233?m\u233? so t\u233?nmorw\u233?n, w\u233?nde efalofifi siy\u233?m Keriso. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Yau eumyotati y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r efe norayat yaufi si f\u233?fefaf. F\u225? so norayat nden\u233? y\u233?mofem efandat f\u233?nat\u233? gh\u233?k\u233?f waing\u233?gh a f\u233?mofem t\u225?f ew\u225?wefnotati njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r\u233?t. F\u225? nemnat f\u225? kar em mer mat, w\u233?nde y\u233?fene emar\u233?gh y\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? mbandm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
F\u225? yau em Kerisoene, efe y\u233?m m\u233?inyotio fifioene s\u233?nko. Yesum ew\u225?ut\u225?ne y\u225?ne \u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i karnyangi y\u233?maf\u233? nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? fifioene s\u233?nkoyam m\u233?inyotio fifi kafekafe ew\u225?ut\u225?ne m\u233?nj\u233?rm\u233?nj\u233?r \u225?rkam\u233? em. Nden\u233? ende y\u233?nd nanotam ndern\u225?ye Ng\u225?nj\u225?n m\u233?nde y\u233?m y\u233?nd s\u225?i nanotam.
