F\u233?m k\u233?r t\u233? emorm\u233?n Kerisof\u233? a ey\u225?toi yuwek k\u233?tam\u233? lim\u225?n\u233?gh mb\u233?rmb\u233?rafeta y\u233?n\u233? mband maratm\u233?n. Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde, n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m so emor nden\u233? f\u233?m em y\u233?n\u233? mband maratm\u233?n? N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?mofem ewaitotati y\u233?n\u233? n\u225?k nden\u233?, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
"Yau yereta y\u233?n\u233?! Yau tufo y\u233?n\u233?! Yau tiy\u225?nja!"? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? n\u225?kn\u225?kam yufarotat ndenanit em mband maratm\u233?n rokar y\u233?nau engnetam a ngawaindangi, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? sem \u225?r wafroghm\u233?n n\u225?kn\u225?kro, a watamegh em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
