F\u233?m t\u233? nanoy\u233?nd Kerisof\u233?, y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde ewafarenati tikfe njafarm\u233?n rokar, \u225?nde Keriso n\u225?mnjoi Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene tamb\u233?n ng\u225?ngata. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Ewafarenati f\u233?fenjo mwighaye njafarm\u233?n rokar, yau y\u233?na mband maratm\u233?n rokar, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m k\u233?r t\u233? emorm\u233?n, a f\u233?fene gh\u233?rs\u233? siy\u233?m etnong Kerisof\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
T\u225?f Keriso, efe y\u233?m f\u233?fene efalo gh\u233?rs\u233?, njam kufarng\u233?, f\u233?m w\u233?i so em y\u233?maf\u233? ndimbal kwayaghayan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Ekmetati krot f\u233?fene mband tik\u233?f: yaufi wal, w\u225?iw\u225?iyam, m\u233?ndm\u233?ndro, yaufi mwigh\u233? a kw\u233?njt\u233?, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m mewangot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u233?kw so y\u233?n\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?m t\u233? tayotau y\u233?n\u233? yaufi yamam\u233?, fronde f\u233?m k\u233?s tamorw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
W\u233?nde s\u233?nonjo f\u233?m k\u233?kmbongi y\u233?n\u233? yamta: n\u233?kw, kw\u233?rnar, m\u233?ndm\u233?nd, wasaligh, a yaufi si oray\u233?gh mb\u237?rmb\u237?re. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Yau t\u225?f engwawinda \u225?mb \u225?rfet, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mofem t\u233? ewitam\u233?nd f\u233?fene t\u225?nd\u225?w\u225?r gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?fenjo wafroghyamafayo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Nawamanetati tot\u233?r gh\u233?rsaye, \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? t\u233? n\u233?namndai tot\u233?r matyam k\u233?nj\u250?n y\u225?ne Wafrogh \u225?roene mbanmbanan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? tot\u233?r gh\u233?rsayan n\u233?m\u233? \u225?mb yau y\u233?na y\u233?m T\u233?ndo \u225?r or Ju \u225?r, gh\u233?ngan n\u233?f\u233?gh \u225?r o gh\u233?ngan n\u233?f\u233?ghofnar \u225?r, d\u225?bi \u225?r, \u225?ronjagh \u225?r, faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r o yuwek \u225?r, w\u233?nde Keriso siy\u233?m m\u233?inyotio, a f\u225? y\u233?mor m\u233?inyotio k\u233?nj\u250?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene kaf\u233?ghm\u233?n \u225?r, nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar a mindefifi uw\u233?ghkaf, nawamanetati f\u233?myo y\u233?naye gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233?, mer, yuwan gh\u233?rs\u233?, meraf\u233? yam a m\u233?tar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Njam \u225?mb f\u233?fene t\u233? ewam \u225?w\u225?taran\u233?gh \u225?mb \u225?rf\u233?, tawawalindang\u233? y\u233?fene yaufi nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Yur\u233? k\u233?s yawalindai f\u233?fene yaufi. \u193?myogh \u225?r aem \u225?mb \u225?rf\u233? a tawawalindang\u233? y\u233?fene yaufi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
A m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? meryamfaf t\u233?fghangi uw\u233?gh, \u225?rk\u233? m\u233?n\u225?yam taumbang\u233? m\u233?inyotio yam \u225?mbiro tikfan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Kerisoene krufr\u225?tam so elimnde f\u233?fene tik\u233?f, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m fifikafe em \u225?mbiro fifiyan f\u233?m t\u233? enmotai y\u233?n\u233? krufr\u225?tfaf f\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n. A so em k\u225?njo ram\u233?ghaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Kerisoene si so y\u233?mor f\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n afoghare nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? nawatametati a naw\u225?utanati f\u233?myo m\u233?inyotio s\u225?fot k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaye. Wagh y\u233?rametati Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf m\u233?naye samse, wafnjagh wagh, a wagh Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?rta k\u225?njo ram\u233?gh tik\u233?faf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
A n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?mofem njam ewafrotati o norayati, ewafrotati m\u233?inyotio Yur\u233? Yesuene y\u233?tkw\u233?nan, yarametati k\u225?njo ram\u233?gh Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Afai y\u225? k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Efalo y\u225?togh \u225?rfene m\u233?r\u233?n gh\u233?rs\u233?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Amaf, n\u225?y\u225?retati f\u233?fenjo \u225?rfefaf, y\u233?n\u233?fai f\u233?mofem tawafrotangi nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
\u193?r, euwetati f\u233?fenjo amaf a yau t\u225?f t\u233?kr\u225?t em y\u233?fefaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Ambum, ey\u225?retati f\u233?fene afaf a amaf m\u233?inyotio efghon, y\u233?nayan n\u225?uwete Yur\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Afaf a amaf, yau n\u233?kwot em\u233?indati ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r, o f\u225? so kuwembangi.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r, ey\u225?retati f\u233?fenjo mbandm\u233?n yur\u233? m\u233?inyotio yaman, a n\u225?s\u225?fotati, yau t\u225?fandro y\u233?fene gh\u233?kfanro m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?fene m\u233?nde wifogh\u233?t, w\u233?nde n\u225?s\u225?fotati efalo tikfe \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m Yur\u233? f\u233?rf\u233?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
N\u233?m\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh njam yafrotati, n\u225?s\u225?fotati m\u233?inyotio f\u233?fene tikfe, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? n\u225?s\u225?fotati Yurai, yau mbandm\u233?n yurai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Nawafarotati nden\u233? Yuram so tawaramang\u233? fai f\u233?fe n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mo t\u233? tawamnde y\u225?ne \u225?r\u233?t. M\u233?nam\u233?n Keriso siy\u233?m efalofifi Yur\u233? f\u233?m n\u225?s\u225?fotati y\u225?yot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
\u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom yafrote m\u225?m\u225?fi so tinjong\u233? w\u233?ndefai y\u225?njo yaufim\u233?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam moghan ekmete m\u233?inyotio \u225?r \u225?mbr\u233?rero.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 4
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Yur\u233?, ewawafrotati f\u233?fenjo faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r\u233?t mbark\u225?ndaye a \u225?mbr\u233?rero, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m mat em nden\u233? f\u233?fene Yur\u233? w\u233?i k\u233?t\u233? y\u233?m njafaran.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 W\u233?ikor waufarogh yam
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
K\u233?tan karamangi Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh k\u233?nj\u250?t, gh\u233?k\u233?f \u233?regh aem a k\u225?njo ram\u233?gh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
A Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayati t\u233?feyot w\u233?i, m\u233?n\u225?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so t\u233?saw\u233?rng\u233? s\u233?safne t\u233?fene si waitogh\u233?t, m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?ndfem so y\u233?ngwaitotam Kerisoene kwankwane yam, y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan y\u233?nd w\u233?nyau kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayati m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?ndon so n\u233?ngafrotan saf\u233?nro, nden\u233? y\u233?ndon so f\u233?t\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Kor k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaye nawarawenati wafroghyaman y\u233?fe tamb\u233?n efe em efalo y\u225?toghofnar, ewafrotati mere m\u233?inyotio \u225?s\u225?fogh f\u233?fene sem y\u233?maf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u233?fene si fia t\u250?m\u233?n tam m\u233?ndef\u233? a wayamneghaf\u233?, m\u233?nat f\u233?mofem so tawaramangi mbark\u225?nd uwangogh m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Ambinom\u233?n \u225?sneghaf\u233? si
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Tukikus\u233?m so ewaufrote m\u233?inyotio si tanem\u233?n. F\u225? siy\u233?m tane f\u250?tar, ndimbal mwighaf\u233? faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r y\u233?ndf\u233? Yurane k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?ndon y\u233?ngw\u225?f\u225?retan f\u225? f\u233?fefaf m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m mat so em y\u233?nd ndern\u225?ye y\u233?nmor y\u233?na a y\u233?mon so ewaw\u233?ngsote f\u233?fene tik\u233?f. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u225? enre y\u233?maf\u233? Onesimusf\u233?, t\u233?fene ndimbal mwigh\u233? k\u233?r ro f\u250?tar, efe w\u233?i y\u233?m f\u233?fenjoyo. Y\u233?mofem so ewaufrot m\u233?inyotio n\u233?m\u233? nufrote y\u233?na.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Aristakus\u233?m, emaf\u233? y\u233?nlaware y\u233?ndf\u233? kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngon, engwawatembete \u225?sneghaf\u233? si, a Mak\u233?m w\u233?i, efe y\u233?m Banabasene y\u225?kal. (F\u233?mofem t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd si y\u225?nem\u233?n, f\u225? njam y\u233?n\u233?m f\u233?fefaf t\u225?f tumyongi.) {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Yesu, efe y\u233?mndetat J\u233?stus, w\u233?i engwawatembete \u225?sneghaf\u233? si. Y\u233?n\u233? nambio \u225?r f\u225?ro Ju \u225?rm\u233?n em tane \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rfefaf Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh k\u233?nj\u250?t, a f\u225? t\u233? tam ndimbal w\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh \u225?r tayot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Efafras, efe \u225?mb y\u233?m f\u233?fenjoyo a Keriso Yesuene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, engwawatembete \u225?sneghaf\u233? si. F\u225? t\u250?m\u233?n yakai Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oraighan f\u233?fe t\u233?fnan, m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m so taikrataye ewakai Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene m\u233?ndefaf, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? sotaf\u233? efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Y\u233?nd nafrotan y\u225?nem\u233?n f\u225? minde n\u225?s\u225?fote f\u233?feyot a y\u233?feyot efe em Laodikia yuwon a Ierafolis yuwon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
T\u233?fene f\u250?tar Luk, efe y\u233?m njokt\u233?, a Demas, y\u233?mofem \u225?sneghaf\u233? si engwawatembend f\u233?fe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Tawaram tane \u225?sneghaf\u233? si y\u233?fe f\u250?tar\u233?t Laodikia yuwon, a amaf Nimfa a Yesuene m\u233?rnat efe n\u225?umendat y\u225?ne m\u233?ngon.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Soram\u233? f\u233?mofem yaftati y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?r\u233?n, mat aem nden\u233? yaftati w\u233?i Laodikia Yesuene m\u233?rnan. Y\u233?n\u233? efghonyo, yaftati tane f\u233?r\u233?n efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r\u233?t Laodikia yuwon y\u233?mofem so tawawatembangi f\u233?fe.
