Y\u233?nd, Fol, y\u233?farotan y\u233?n\u233? \u225?sneghaf\u233? si tanjo ng\u225?ngaye. Wafarotati Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh tayot njam y\u233?nd w\u233?m kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngon. Ng\u225?r\u225?m so y\u233?m f\u233?fefaf.}
